Cell["\<\
How to read helicity expansion: 
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]sa\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] is the helicity component, \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]sac\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] the conjugate. Helicity \
eigenstate is the value of the first slot. Second slot is a label for \
multiplicities which can be ignored in interpreting the propagation. So the \
combo sa[-3, 1] sac[-3, 1 ] signal the propagation of helicity 3!
\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.983000953530922*^9, 3.983000962831609*^9}, {
  3.9830009977157793`*^9, 
  3.983001107562572*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"cf1200b4-2176-4442-8617-\
9a377bee901c"],

