Cell["\<\
Call to SourceDeclare in order to produce the rules morphing a tensor into \
its components. Only needs to be called once unless new fields are used. If \
it is no used, CompSatProp will compute the rules at every run.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.982992065008794*^9, 
